mes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_geo">以色列</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_geo">俄罗斯</category><media:content height="1800" medium="image" url="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2023/11/21/multimedia/21israel-gps-promo-a-lfpv/21israel-gps-promo-a-lfpv-mediumSquareAt3X.jpg" width="1800"></media:content><media:credit>谢尔盖·波诺马列夫为《纽约时报》撰稿</media:credit></item><item><title>以色列人和巴勒斯坦人之间致命的心理鸿沟正在扩大</title><link/>https://www.nytimes.com/2023/11/20/world/middleeast/israelis-palestinians-conflict.html<guid ispermalink="true"> https://www.nytimes.com/2023/11/20/world/middleeast/israelis-palestinians-conflict.html </guid><atom:link href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/11/20/world/middleeast/israelis-palestinians-conflict.html" rel="standout"></atom:link><description>在一场双方完全不理解的冲突中，双方都失去了将对方视为人类的能力。</description><dc:creator>罗杰·科恩</dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 11:54:04 +0000</pubDate><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">以色列-加沙战争 (2023- )</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">巴勒斯坦人</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">恐怖主义</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">犹太人和犹太教</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">阿以战争 (1948)</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">大屠杀和纳粹时代</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">宗教与信仰</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org">哈马斯</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_per">伊塔玛·本·格维尔</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_per">摩西·达扬</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_per">马哈茂德·扎哈尔</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_geo">以色列</category><media:content height="1799" medium="image" url="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2023/11/20/multimedia/20israel-palestinians-psychology-top-tvfh/20israel-palestinians-psychology-top-tvfh-mediumSquareAt3X.jpg" width="1800"></media:content><media:credit>阿菲夫·阿米雷 (Afif Amireh) 为《纽约时报》撰稿</media:credit><media:description>十月，以色列安全部队在耶路撒冷观看巴勒斯坦人的祈祷。附近是犹太人和穆斯林的圣地，多年来一直是紧张局势的焦点之一。</media:description></item><item><title>加沙医院的危机等</title><link/>https://www.nytimes.com/2023/11/21/podcasts/gazas-hospital-trump.html<guid ispermalink="true"> https://www.nytimes.com/2023/11/21/podcasts/gazas-hospital-trump.html </guid><atom:link href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/11/21/podcasts/gazas-hospital-trump.html" rel="standout"></atom:link><description>此外，联邦法院采取行动削弱《投票权法案》，并给城市带来了无人驾驶出租车的压力。</description><dc:creator>纽约时报音频</dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 11:03:34 +0000</pubDate><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">医院</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">2024 年总统选举</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_geo">以色列</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_geo">加沙地带</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org">希法医院（加沙地带）</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org">世界卫生组织</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">投票权、登记和要求</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">投票权法 (1965)</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">出租车和出租车司机</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org">韦莫</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org">谷歌公司</category><media:content height="1518" medium="image" url="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2023/11/21/podcasts/21Headlines-indonesian-treatment/21Headlines-indonesian-treatment-mediumSquareAt3X.jpg" width="1519"></media:content><media:credit>阿纳斯·谢里夫/路透社</media:credit><media:description>本月早些时候，加沙的印度尼西亚医院。该飞地有36家医院。</media:description></item><item><title>史蒂夫·乔布斯的阴影笼罩着 OpenAI 的混乱局面</title><link/>https://www.nytimes.com/2023/11/21/technology/sam-altman-steve-jobs.html<guid ispermalink="true"> https://www.nytimes.com/2023/11/21/technology/sam-altman-steve-jobs.html </guid><atom:link href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/11/21/technology/sam-altman-steve-jobs.html" rel="standout"></atom:link><description>人工智能最著名的推动者萨姆·奥尔特曼 (Sam Altman) 了解到，要成为像苹果传奇人物那样有远见的创始人是很困难的。</description><dc:creator>大卫·斯特雷菲尔德</dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 08:00:12 +0000</pubDate><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_per">塞缪尔·H·奥特曼</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_per">乔布斯，史蒂文·P</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org">开放人工智能实验室</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org">苹果公司</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org">微软公司</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">人工智能</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">初创企业</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">创业精神</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">任命和高管变动</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_per">凯尔·沃格特</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org">邮轮有限责任公司</category><media:content height="1798" medium="image" url="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2023/11/20/multimedia/20microsoft-openai-lpwt/20microsoft-openai-lpwt-mediumSquareAt3X-v2.jpg" width="1800"></media:content><media:credit>吉姆·威尔逊/纽约时报</media:credit><media:description>史蒂夫·乔布斯在被边缘化和离开十多年后重返苹果公司，这对其他科技公司的创始人来说是一个诱人但又不可能的比较。</media:description></item><item><title> OpenAI 的混乱 + 我们对 Sam Altman 的采访</title><link/>https://www.nytimes.com/2023/11/20/podcasts/mayhem-at-openai-our-interview-with-sam-altman.html<guid ispermalink="true"> https://www.nytimes.com/2023/11/20/podcasts/mayhem-at-openai-our-interview-with-sam-altman.html </guid><atom:link href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/11/20/podcasts/mayhem-at-openai-our-interview-with-sam-altman.html" rel="standout"></atom:link><description>科技界最疯狂的周末。</description><dc:creator>凯文·罗斯、凯西·牛顿、戴维斯·兰德、雷切尔·科恩、珍·波扬特、罗温·尼米斯托、丹·鲍威尔和马里昂·洛扎诺</dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 02:26:48 +0000</pubDate><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">科学和技术</category><media:content height="1799" medium="image" url="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2023/11/20/multimedia/20HF-altman-ms-gfwk/20HF-altman-ms-gfwk-mediumSquareAt3X-v3.jpg" width="1800"></media:content><media:credit>图片插图来自《纽约时报》；照片：埃里克·里斯伯格/美联社</media:credit></item><item><title>OpenAI 的混乱状况解释</title><link/>https://www.nytimes.com/2023/11/21/briefing/open-ai-sam-altman-microsoft.html<guid ispermalink="true"> https://www.nytimes.com/2023/11/21/briefing/open-ai-sam-altman-microsoft.html </guid><atom:link href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/11/21/briefing/open-ai-sam-altman-microsoft.html" rel="standout"></atom:link><description>对未来的恐惧如何导致了科技界的政变。</description><dc:creator>凯文·罗斯</dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 11:39:50 +0000</pubDate><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">内部故事情节-否</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org">开放人工智能实验室</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_per">塞缪尔·H·奥特曼</category><media:content height="1799" medium="image" url="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2023/11/21/multimedia/21themorning-lead-1promo/21themorning-lead-1-hjcm-mediumSquareAt3X.jpg" width="1800"></media:content><media:credit>吉姆·威尔逊/纽约时报</media:credit><media:description>萨姆·奥特曼.</media:description></item><item><title> OpenAI 表明人工智能可能存在固有的治理问题</title><link/>https://www.nytimes.com/2023/11/21/business/dealbook/openai-corporate-governance-altman-board.html<guid ispermalink="true"> https://www.nytimes.com/2023/11/21/business/dealbook/openai-corporate-governance-altman-board.html </guid><atom:link href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/11/21/business/dealbook/openai-corporate-governance-altman-board.html" rel="standout"></atom:link><description> OpenAI 错综复杂的结构在设计上就很复杂，正是它导致了萨姆·奥尔特曼 (Sam Altman) 的下台。</description><dc:creator>安德鲁·罗斯·索尔金、拉维·马图、伯恩哈德·华纳、莎拉·凯斯勒、迈克尔·J·德拉·默塞德、劳伦·赫希和埃弗拉特·利夫尼</dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 13:17:57 +0000</pubDate><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">内部故事情节-否</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">人工智能</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">道德与官员不当行为</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org">开放人工智能实验室</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org">人类人工智能有限责任公司</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_per">塞缪尔·H·奥特曼</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org">微软公司</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org">Salesforce.com公司</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org">兴盛资本</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org">老虎全球管理有限公司</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_per">马克·贝尼奥夫</category><media:content height="1801" medium="image" url="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2023/11/21/multimedia/21db-altman-mzlj/21db-altman-mzlj-mediumSquareAt3X.jpg" width="1800"></media:content><media:credit>贾斯汀沙利文/盖蒂图片社</media:credit><media:description>整个科技界都听到了这样的人事变动：OpenAI 被罢免的首席执行官萨姆·奥尔特曼 (Sam Altman) 现在为微软的萨蒂亚·纳德拉 (Satya Nadella) 工作。</media:description></item><item><title>人工智能杀手无人机正在成为现实。各国在限制上存在分歧。</title><link/> https://www.nytimes.com/2023/11/21/us/politics/ai-drones-war-law.html<guid ispermalink=